text: Desmiphora cayennensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Tavakilian and Néouze in 2004. It is known from French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora cayennensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 2004
